text: Michelle Borth (born August 19, 1978) is an American actress. She is known for her roles on The Forgotten and the HBO series Tell Me You Love Me. Borth played Catherine Rollins on the CBS crime-drama Hawaii Five-0. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Actors from New York City
